summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4623 for the improvement of 17th Avenue Southwest, from West Marginal Way to the north line of Sanders 2nd Addition to West Seattle; by grading and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 53779, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
